{"tid":1333564,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"7月1日 有個關鍵位好似冇人講過","createTime":"2019-07-19T18:05:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T18:19:35.000Z","uid":61443,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"202d48b0602eb9e36c46ddea613982f176f52257","tid":1333564,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T18:05:13.000Z","msg":"因為班暴徒要搞升旗禮<br />\n所以晨咁早就出咗去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然佢地失敗咗 <br />\n但係09左右就去搞馬路 <br />\n聚下人氣搞呢搞路<br />\n所以下午就搞到立法會 <br />\n撬埋閘 夜晚開party <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為班暴徒都知<br />\n12點要趕尾班車<br />\n玩到呢個鍾數一定走咗大班人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n班暴徒之所以成功<br />\n歸功於晨咁早搞事第一批人 <br />\n如果佢地下午先開始搞<br />\n玩到 12點 最多都仲係撬緊閘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利伸：支持警察 維持治安 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"160211eb51f426687177844855474f05fe1dbbf8","tid":1333564,"uid":74058,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T18:08:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76d326fb02aa96a01b86c64bf294788683c2c035","tid":1333564,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T18:09:02.000Z","msg":"今次一輸就係大搜捕，中共加緊控制香港，進一步收窄言論自由同新聞自由，唔可能再有真普選既機會，香港人甚至會好似新疆人咁!!<br />\n<br />\n只能說是背水一戰，我地開左個波，要收手都已經太遲，香港人輸唔起，<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">一輸就會連飯碗、港元、安穩生活甚至生命都輸埋</span></strong>!!!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以要早!!!"},{"pid":"e8732c70e61129281da9371bcf6cce9d496e7c08","tid":1333564,"uid":74058,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T18:12:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23900fc810728bcff3aea51d4b49619a75b2ff6b","tid":1333564,"uid":174174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco